{"tid":42844,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"A7R II定A7S II","createTime":"2016-12-17T04:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T16:19:20.000Z","uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c381cdf9f8d75366552eb2e1fb1ea2783fe8b3e","tid":42844,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"細佬對拍戲睇電影好有趣<br />\n好彩大學讀到關拍片既科<br />\n自己一直都有拍野<br />\n有時都會同女朋友去影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但用到既機同鏡都係係學校到借<br />\n用開6D<br />\n升上去讀開始發覺成日要係學校借好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想自己擁有一部<br />\n好啦正題<br />\n聽人講拍片就a7s2<br />\n我好多同學都用/想買a7s2<br />\n但又因為我都想用部機黎影相<br />\n所以一直糾結緊s定r好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地覺得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f41b05e38b15cd0be0acec721d86d13cdae7b28","tid":42844,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"a7rii"},{"pid":"6168ed3b0b7dc6b27e15e5f8194195b4ca901750","tid":42844,"uid":26122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"大學咩科？"},{"pid":"802ef802c02b758494109cd558a56a2d848d2e5b","tid":42844,"uid":26122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"拍片我會用gh4 + speedbooster + sigma 18-35mm"},{"pid":"95b53a5ef5445105eda862ad3e0caf4e5bb32fe5","tid":42844,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>a7rii</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇多d原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb9af82e5f98847a85653acb4e45cc61061ae1e","tid":42844,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學咩科？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理大設計"},{"pid":"a4e5578fe3fb4f6d1e0624ec066