/>\n影風景個d阿 唔係幫女朋友影mk相個d <br />\nbtw s2影相到比起6d好定差？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23533bc978aaabb7e45318ab983fdee6261eca99","tid":42844,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>A7rii 個解象度同dynamic range都俾較大同高，而且無反機輕過單反機隻手無咁易勞損，你其實上其他網睇少少research就知rii同sii個分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有做research ar 我自己都偏向 r2 但拍片個到好似s2表現真係會好d 之後係utube又睇左條片話其實太多pixel都唔係好事 所以係到求問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你夜晚or陰暗環境拍片多唔多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現階段唔多 因為我仲係新手 打燈個到未太學識 但將來會想拍多d陰暗 因為我覺得好有feel 同埋自己都好唔鍾意個d較到畫面好光個d大眾口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7484393891887e4668f1941bb95aa5b92fa4cc","tid":42844,"uid":2123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有做research ar 我自己都偏向 r2 但拍片個到好似s2表現真係會好d 之後係utube又睇左條片話其實太多pixel都唔係好事 所以係到求問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你夜晚or陰暗環境拍片多唔多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現階段唔多 因為我仲係新手 打燈個到未太學識 但將來會想拍多d陰暗 因為我覺得好有feel 同埋自己都好唔鍾意個d較到畫面好光個d大眾口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如你諗吓自己需唔需要a7rii嘅超高像數先，拍片就一定係a7sii好啲"},{"pid":"e748cf84585f54609f0f6175981f10276f7a0373","tid":42844,"uid":43904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"新手借問，點解拍片一定揀7sii, 關iso事？"},{"pid":"d2240b859b81ec0ddfd68b1780af91711f453a86","tid":42844,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大學咩科？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理大設計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師弟你好"},{"pid":"749ec2ca62c97dd0819f4129affba40e24ce7952","tid":42844,"uid":33130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"得7s2有得拍Slog3<br />\n<br />\n你自己考慮"},{"pid":"a7ebb2c04e9702ffedaecafe1451dcfb6d65a713","tid":42844,"uid":67855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"兩部都用過，如果你真係第時用黎想拍片，而又真係想用sony，就A7S2啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過頭先都有巴打提到GH4個組合都可以考慮下，出面都唔少人用，而且價錢應該平啲添（應該係）"},{"pid":"ef4a0e62f5acbe4857e997bb371890a838c368b7","tid":42844,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩部都用過，如果你真係第時用黎想拍片，而又真係想用sony，就A7S2啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過頭先都有巴打提到GH4個組合都可以考慮下，出面都唔少人用，而且價錢應該平啲添（應該係）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果a6500&amp;a7ii呢 細佬因為d事少左budget<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb7d87901d96a46f21c40d1e7aefae4500c3b22","tid":42844,"uid":67855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩部都用過，如果你真係第時用黎想拍片，而又真係想用sony，就A7S2啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過頭先都有巴打提到GH4個組合都可以考慮下，出面都唔少人用，而且價錢應該平啲添（應該係）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果a6500&amp;a7ii呢 細佬因為d事少左budgetundefined undefined</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我唔太清楚, 就咁上網睇過資料，啲人話A6500 rolling shutter 好嚴重，同埋機身冇得mon聲, 要external 駁野解決...<br />\n<br />\n但佢就多少少野玩囉...拍到少少slow motion...(雖然好雞肋) 同埋AF 堅係快"},{"pid":"e897717492a3f017e73ff9d40924d1b8148d166b","tid":42844,"uid":16757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:46:15.000Z","msg":"其實而加邊部相機拍片係最靚 真心想知"},{"pid":"5ed70a063ef45f7d4a0a40a33d210bc4205c1300","tid":42844,"uid":14875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大學咩科？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理大設計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ndm??"},{"pid":"ddf2aadf2d291c319cfbc13f050506e7fe7b3b53","tid":42844,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T19:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實而加邊部相機拍片係最靚 真心想知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點先為止靚？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dpreview.com/reviews/image-comparison/fullscreen?attr29_0=sony_a7s&amp;attr29_1=canon_xc10&amp;attr72_0=1080&amp;attr72_1=1080&amp;normalization=full&amp;widget=383&amp;x=0.7628788555813902&amp;y=-0.8494208494208495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dpreview.com%2Freviews%2Fimage-comparison%2Ffullscreen%3Fattr29_0%3Dsony_a7s%26attr29_1%3Dcanon_xc10%26attr72_0%3D1080%26attr72_1%3D1080%26normalization%3Dfull%26widget%3D383%26x%3D0.7628788555813902%26y%3D-0.8494208494208495&d=4XQIVCbeeCMwHoKAx8ePbQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f3995b69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dpreview.com/reviews/image-comparison/fullscreen?attr29_0=sony_a7s&amp;attr29_1=canon_xc10&amp;attr72_0=1080&amp;attr72_1=1080&amp;normalization=full&amp;widget=383&amp;x=0.7628788555813902&amp;y=-0.8494208494208495</a>"},{"pid":"dee8a6c5bd78b1cc7a18805ef271bc2a6c7e2b2a","tid":42844,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T19:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兩部都用過，如果你真係第時用黎想拍片，而又真係想用sony，就A7S2啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過頭先都有巴打提到GH4個組合都可以考慮下，出面都唔少人用，而且價錢應該平啲添（應該係）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁如果a6500&amp;amp;a7ii呢 細佬因為d事少左budgetundefined undefined</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我唔太清楚, 就咁上網睇過資料，啲人話A6500 rolling shutter 好嚴重，同埋機身冇得mon聲, 要external 駁野解決...<br />\n<br />\n但佢就多少少野玩囉...拍到少少slow motion...(雖然好雞肋) 同埋AF 堅係快</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似較下shutter speed情況就會好翻d 不過rolling shutter好似a72 a7s2 a6x00都幾明顯<br />\n<br />\n聲個到唔算太大問題 因為多數都係用boom mic或者wireless收音 <br />\n<br />\n我宜家就糾結緊full fram同aspc既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f824fcf648b4754fcaaa890b320b8f8acb709c","tid":42844,"uid":52210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T19:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大學咩科？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理大設計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ndm??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔話你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}